 head office and business  technology centers global coverage management management profile environmental social  governance environmental social and governance report employees  workplace quality sustainable operating practices environmental protection community investment job opportunities contact us head office business  technology center location map company profile  about us  company profile  solomon systech limited is a leading semiconductor company providing display ic products and system solutions on an international basis under its own global brand adopting a fabless business model the group specializes in the design development and sales of proprietary ic products that enable a wide range of display applications for smartphones smart tvs and other smart devices including consumer electronics products wearables portable devices and industrial appliances     the group has a high caliber and experienced design team to develop its own intellectual properties ip for highly integrated display ic products and total system solutions including   mobile display driver ic ddi  incell touch display driver ic tddi maxtouch® oncell  outcell touch controller ic mipi bridge ic display controller ic  large ddi  oled ddi bistable ddi oled lighting driver ic  given a design team with indepth experience senior management personnel of over twenty years of experience in the global semiconductor industry a broad product portfolio covering nearly all kinds of display technologies and dedicated design centers in different regions plus a worldwide sales and distribution network solomon systech has become one of the major display ic suppliers in the world supporting global customers with proprietary display ic products and total system solutions   the group serves many bluechip clients and has received numerous awards from its customers suppliers industrial organizations as well as the investment community the groups shares were listed on the main board of the stock exchange of hong kong limited on  april  hkse    corporate backgrounder   the group has two key business units namely main display and advanced display the main display business focuses on mainstream display solutions including mobile touch mobile driver mobile interface as well as large display products the advanced display business includes oled display and lighting products as well as bistable display products   disclaimer  job opportunities  sitemap  contact us  copyright  solomon systech all rights reserved product engineer  solomon systech limited  jobsdb hong kong   ☰ menu jobsdb solomon systech limited we are a leading flat panel display ic company for hightech products providing display ic solutions on an international basis under our own global brand with a fabless business model the group specializes in the design development and sales of proprietary ic solutions that enable a wide range of display applications for cellular phones computer monitors flat panel tvs and other innovative products we invite high calibre to join a core team of highly talented and well trained professionals with us product engineer aug jobsdb ref jhk employer ref pehk tools save this job share print this job ad report this job job responsibilities manage projects on developing new ic products perform ic evaluation characterization and qualification application support to customers with occasional travel prepare ic specification and documentation   job requirements bachelor degree or above in electronic engineering computer engineering engineering physics applied science or equivalent  years working experience or above in product development or electronics application experience in flat panel display industry oled  tftlcd is advantageous experience in pads schematic capture pcb layout and autocad skills application knowledge on visual basic c or c programming be proactive and have strong analytic and problem solving skill fluent english and chinese mandarin with good report writing presentation 